'''Jeh''' was a [[H'kig]] [[glyph]] that represented a mystical ideal of the peaceful religion. Considered too sacred to be written in full, the glyph was often abbreviated as ''J<nowiki>'</nowiki>'', as in the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[J't'p'tan]]. The symbol could be translated roughly as "the imminent" in [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]], and was a mystical reference in the [[H'kig]] religion.<ref name="Wizards">{{Wizards|url=default.asp?x=starwars/article/sw20030130jtptan|text=J't'p'tan: Temples and Tybis}}</ref>

